---
// 8. Audience — who it's for (cards reveal on scroll).
---
<section class="audience" id="audience">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title" data-i18n="audience.title">Lingo7 Realty is for you if you…</h2>
    <div class="audience__grid">
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-english">Struggle with the material in English → read every paragraph with a translation and grasp the meaning right away</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-failed">Have failed, or fear failing, because of the language → the language barrier is gone right inside the questions and explanations</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-retain">Worry you won't keep it all in your head → adaptive tests find the gaps, and spaced repetition locks them in by exam day</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-immigrant">Are building a real estate career as an immigrant → pass the exam and build your professional English along the way</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-time">Are short on time — 10–15 minutes a day → the textbook, tests, and math in one app, in short sessions</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
